  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="2" name="MSG_002_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}But... I...![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="3" name="MND_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}She sounds upset...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Maybe I should just let her in.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 61 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}Thank goodness...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 61 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}I'm so happy to see you again.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}I'm sorry to show up so suddenly...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}But... I really needed to talk to you.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="SEL_006_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Почуваюся добре.]]></Option>
