  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}I... remember everything.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}It seems like everyone else has forgotten, but I remember...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 10 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 10 25 25}That day, we...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="SEL_008_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Yeah, we did.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Don't cry.]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 10 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 10 25 25}I'm sorry...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}It's just that, when I remembered...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}I was afraid you might go somewhere far away, like you did during the last battle...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="SEL_010_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}I'm not going anywhere.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}......]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}Today is graduation day... isn't it?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}I'm sorry... The ceremony's already begun.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 1 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 1 25 25}The weather is so nice outside.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 1 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 1 25 25}Do you remember where we all promised to meet?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 1 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 1 25 25}Why don't we go ahead and wait for the others?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 1 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 19 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 1 25 25}We can enjoy the peaceful view of the city.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
